{"tid":1109440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港個天經常多雲灰濛濛 係咪空氣污染特別嚴重","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T03:22:15.000Z","uid":229468,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"95c9a3e7951399553ba18785d09cee78d7e10662","tid":1109440,"uid":229468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"去過好多地方旅行<br />\n遠啲嘅例如澳洲歐洲 <br />\n個天好多時都一舊雲都冇<br />\n一片蔚藍陽光普照<br />\n嗰種陽光 <br />\n同香港嘅光線好唔同<br />\n非常光鮮亮麗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即是近啲嘅<br />\n日本韓國<br />\n都好多時可以見到個天萬里無雲<br />\n一片蔚藍 陽光普照<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n每次飛返香港<br />\n差唔多每一次<br />\n飛機降落嘅時候<br />\n都要穿過好厚嘅雲層<br />\n飛機係咁震<br />\n穿過雲層 見到灰濛濛嘅大海<br />\n最後係充滿煙霞嘅赤鱲角機場降落<br />\n<br />\n除咗深秋嗰幾個禮拜<br />\n香港可以見到藍天<br />\n其他時候即時出太陽<br />\n個天都係灰濛濛 好多雲<br />\n<br />\n空氣污染真係好嚴重? 還是因為香港氣候地形特別，所以特別多雲同埋煙霞？"},{"pid":"bbe953a79fc0608da6688394d5cbb7b5bed3fc0f","tid":1109440,"uid":229468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244497516875a07a672129e7b73fc007b1bf1610","tid":1109440,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"中共送大禮囉"},{"pid":"a94dc5cad258797d60bb27535c507aa426764078","tid":1109440,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"點解仲要問&quot;係咪&quot;"},{"pid":"a2441c0e7b3f8cefba32097f38994137a6568cae","tid":1109440,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"就算無乜雲既日子都睇到有層野係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116823463784ba603029b0ed952f0c1a1cfbce36","tid":1109440,"uid":5546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"54a8ce952a204fa68914f3e3f69417fa9f71f3aa","tid":1109440,"uid":37586,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"煙霞